His W change really messed up his jungle ganking, but I've still found a bit of success with him in the jungle after the changes. Have to ambush the enemy from behind now instead of charging from the side with W

Seriously though, you REALLY don't want to see Blitzcrank become a viable solo laner. He scales VERY well with items, and Hydra is amazing for AD Blitz anyways because of the active and massive synergy with his E allowing him to triple attack. You really don't need a botrk because you're aiming to kill the enemy ADC/Assassin/Mage. Not necessarily the tanks

